description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join an established Community Learning Disability Team. The post holder will hold a clinical caseload of adults with Learning Disabilities in Swanseaw.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alongside working with individuals with epilepsy, mental health issues, challenging behaviour and complex health you will be supported to gain valuable clinical skills and experience. The post holder will also work in partnership with primary and secondary healthcare colleagues and other stakeholders.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Applicant will be a Registered Learning Disability Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Elizabeth FairLead Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
